{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-js","path":"/development/2021/12/21/react-conf-2021-recap/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"React Conference 2021 - State of their Art React Conf Website Feature Recap Concurrent Features implement Concurrent renderer in React 1â€¦","frontmatter":{"title":"React Conference 2021 - State of their Art","subtitle":"Vision is the art of seeing what is invisible to others. - Jonathan Swift","date":"December 21, 2021","author":"Mark Roxberry","featured":true,"tags":["react","conference","coder"],"postimage":{"alt":"React Logo banner image","src":{"absolutePath":"/home/runner/work/gatsby-roxberry/gatsby-roxberry/temp/src/posts/2021-12-21-react-conf-2021-recap/post.png","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fullWidth","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/fd6b6db9a35f4cb73bec6222d81623d9/c2d17/post.png","srcSet":"/static/fd6b6db9a35f4cb73bec6222d81623d9/76a4f/post.png 750w,\n/static/fd6b6db9a35f4cb73bec6222d81623d9/c2d17/post.png 800w","sizes":"100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/fd6b6db9a35f4cb73bec6222d81623d9/2b382/post.avif 750w,\n/static/fd6b6db9a35f4cb73bec6222d81623d9/6ee87/post.avif 800w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/fd6b6db9a35f4cb73bec6222d81623d9/66907/post.webp 750w,\n/static/fd6b6db9a35f4cb73bec6222d81623d9/0d27e/post.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"100vw"}]},"width":1,"height":0.75},"resize":{"src":"/static/fd6b6db9a35f4cb73bec6222d81623d9/f3583/post.png","height":900,"width":1200}}}}},"html":"<h2>React Conference 2021 - State of their Art</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://conf.reactjs.org\">React Conf Website</a></p>\n<h3>Feature Recap</h3>\n<h4>Concurrent Features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>implement Concurrent renderer in React 18 with no (known) breaking changes</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Suspense and Server Components</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>granular component streaming from the server</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Developer Notes</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>new React DevTools team</li>\n<li>new Timeline Profiler for debugging</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>React 18 RC</h4>\n<p>Available for feedback:</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">npm install react@rc react-dom@rc</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Change entry to use <em>createRoot</em></p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk3\">// before</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">container</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk12\">document</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">getElementById</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;root&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk12\">ReactDOM</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">render</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk10\">App</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk17\">/&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk12\">container</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk3\">// after</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">container</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk12\">document</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">getElementById</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;root&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">root</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk12\">ReactDOM</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">createRoot</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">container</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk12\">root</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">render</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk10\">App</span><span class=\"mtk17\">/&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>References</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://conf.reactjs.org\">React Conf Website</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://reactjs.org/blog/2021/12/17/react-conf-2021-recap.html\">React Conf 2021 Recap</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://reactjs.org/blog/2021/06/08/the-plan-for-react-18.html\">The Plan for React 18</a></p>\n<h3>Image Credit</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/crud-using-react-41d047224e26/\">React Banner from Free Code Camp post</a></p>\n<h3>Quote Credit</h3>\n<p>Jonathan Swift Quotes. (n.d.). BrainyQuote.com. Retrieved December 21, 2021, from <a href=\"https://www.brainyquote.com/quotes/jonathan_swift_122246\">BrainyQuote.com</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"./IMG_0194.JPG\" alt=\"freecodecamp Photo\"></p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8p